data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 3.87% Absolutely stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with solar on an oversized lot, boasting a wealth of desirable features and a fantastic layout. This residence is the epitome of spaciousness, comfort, and convenience, making it the perfect place to call home.    As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the well-designed layout that combines style and functionality. The main floor features a guest bedroom that can also serve as a versatile office space, ideal for remote work or accommodating guests. The open-concept living areas create a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining, and living room, making it perfect for family gatherings or entertaining friends.    The chef's dream kitchen is a highlight of this home, with ample counter space for meal preparation and a breakfast bar for quick bites. Modern appliances and sleek cabinetry make this space as practical as it is beautiful.    Upstairs, you'll find the primary bedroom suite, which offers a private sanctuary with a spacious ensuite bathroom, providing a serene retreat after a long day. This layout offers additional privacy and separation from the secondary bedrooms, making it a perfect retreat.    The remaining three bedrooms on the upper level are generously sized and equipped with spacious closets, ensuring everyone in the family has their own private space. The shared bathrooms are beautifully appointed, with high-end fixtures and ample storage.    For those who love organization and storage, this home truly excels. Abundant storage space is available throughout the property, from walk-in closets to the oversized 2-car garage, making it effortless to keep everything tidy and clutter-free.    Outside, the oversized lot provides a canvas for your landscaping dreams. Whether you want to create a lush garden, add a play area, or build a relaxing outdoor oasis, the possibilities are endless.
